premise_source_doc_sentence: Red Velvet  (  band  )  , a South Korean girl group .
Red Velvet was formed by the Korean entertainment company S.M. Entertainment in 2014 , and consists of five members .

Prior to joining Red Velvet in 2003 , Manerson was general manager of Real Deal Entertainment , senior vice president of marketing and promotions for Platinum Records , national director of retail for Columbia Records and Northeast regional gospel promoter for A&M Records .
He is president and CEO of Red Velvet Entertainment , a Los Angeles and Atlanta-based boutique management and consulting company .
Red Velvet  (  Hangul : 레드벨벳  )  is a South Korean girl group formed by S.M. Entertainment .
